{"name":"Larmes de minuit (ingestion)","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Une créature qui ingère ce poison ne souffre d'aucun effet... jusqu'à ce que sonne le premier coup de minuit. Si le poison n'a pas été neutralisé auparavant, la créature doit faire un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Constitution DD 17. Si elle échoue, elle subit 31 (9d6) dégâts de poison, la moitié seulement si elle réussit.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Créatures et Oppositions","quantity":1,"weight":0.2,"price":1500,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Très Rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["9d6","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":17,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"poison"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/potions/unique-7.jpg","_id":"pNiGNSFLmYgZMATX"}
{"name":"Poison drow (blessure)","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>En règle générale, les drows sont les seuls à fabriquer ce poison et seulement en des lieux très éloignés de la lumière du soleil. Une créature soumise à ce poison doit réussir un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Constitution DD 13 ou se trouver&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#empoisonne\">empoisonnée</a>&nbsp;pendant 1 heure. Si elle rate son jet de 5 ou plus, elle est&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#inconscient\">inconsciente</a>&nbsp;tout le temps que dure l'empoisonnement. Elle se réveille si elle subit des dégâts ou si une tierce personne utilise son action pour la réveiller en la secouant.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Créatures et Oppositions","quantity":1,"weight":0.2,"price":200,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu Courant","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":13,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"poison"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/potions/unique-2.jpg","_id":"t3HqiTFQJhi5hZY4"}
{"name":"Poison de vouivre (blessure)","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Ce poison se récolte sur une vouivre morte ou&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#neutralise\">neutralisée</a>. Une créature soumise à ce poison doit faire un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Constitution DD 15. Si elle échoue, elle subit 24 (7d6) dégâts de poison, la moitié seulement si elle réussit.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Créatures et Oppositions","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":1200,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Très Rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["7d6","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"poison"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/violet_24.jpg","_id":"utI12DiXr2aXFOrz"}
{"name":"Sang d'assassin (ingestion)","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Une créature soumise à ce poison doit faire un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Constitution DD 10. Si elle le rate, elle subit 6 (1d12) dégâts de poison et elle est&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#empoisonne\">empoisonnée</a>&nbsp;pendant 24 heures. Si elle le réussit, elle subit la moitié des dégâts seulement et elle n'est pas&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#empoisonne\">empoisonnée</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Créatures et Oppositions","quantity":1,"weight":0.2,"price":150,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu courant","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d12","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":10,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"poison"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/blood_03.jpg","_id":"xqmPGodarMZPSPKm"}
